Name:
* Maria Abakumova RUS disqualified from the competition for doping in accordance with Court of Arbitration (CAS)’s final decision of July 2018 and  Athletics Integrity Unit's  “Global List of Ineligible Persons”. Results annulled from 21.08.08 to 20.08.12 and ineligibility  period until 17.05.20. 




Women's Javelin throw - Athletics - Beijing 2008 Summer Olympics
Event Format:
     
     Athletes competed in a qualifying round followed by the final. Top twelve and ties in the qualifying round and all those reaching the announced qualification limit advanced to the final. In the final all finalists were given three tries. The top eight were then given three more. Event facts: Women's Javelin throw competition was held at the Beijing National Stadium and 54 athletes participated in the event.
